  "title": "Packer/ Sorter (Warehouse）",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Gross Salary: Up to $3,500++</strong></u></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for sorting, selecting, weighing, packing (shrink-wrapping), and labeling fresh vegetables and fruits, as well as all other warehouse items (including rice, noodles, grains, cooking oil, meat, etc.)</li><li>Assist with warehouse cleanliness, housekeeping, and storage location organization</li><li>Complete any other tasks assigned by supervisors</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Good communication</li><li>Basic unit conversion skills are preferred (e.g. 1 kg = 1000 g)</li><li>6-day work week (rotating shifts)</li><li>Comfortable working in a cold-room environment </li></ul>",
